{"tid":1079152,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"有無人鍾意河原温On Kawara","createTime":"2019-03-26T17:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T19:50:00.000Z","uid":227172,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"994359c2482af2f241b898f914b63c1e471b1d22","tid":1079152,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"佢好多作品都係研究人同時間嘅關係<br />\n人不能控制自己出現喺邊一段時間<br />\n不能控制時間流動嘅方向<br />\n所以紀錄係我地唯一可以抗衡時間流逝嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n佢做嘅嘢其中一個作品係叫Today Series嘅概念藝術<br />\n當時河原温喺東京，紐約同世界好多不同地方生活<br />\n佢紀錄時間嘅方式係一日畫一幅畫<br />\n上面寫上當日日期<br />\n日期格式同語言根據佢嘅所在地嘅慣用格式寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.guggenheim.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/onkawara_date_paintings.jpg?w=870\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.guggenheim.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F02%2Fonkawara_date_paintings.jpg%3Fw%3D870&h=f3c608a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://uk.phaidon.com/resource/cvr-070-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.phaidon.com%2Fresource%2Fcvr-070-1.jpg&h=b66b1763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫會放喺一個盒<br />\n盒裡面仲會有一張當日同當地嘅新聞<br />\n如果當日內無法完成作品，就要掉咗佢<br />\n喺50年裡面佢做咗3000件紀錄<br />\n<br />\n概念藝術嘅中心就係個概念<br />\n而我個人就覺得佢個概念好美麗<br />\n當然可能好多人唔覺得佢做嘅嘢係藝術<br />\n<br />\n大家可以隨便comment，隨便屌"},{"pid":"833a1044c82202bfd9f4e0131927edce52e412e0","tid":1079152,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"53bcee0a5e59f70a4cc5c22951e089904d63db21","tid":1079152,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833a1044c82202bfd9f4e0131927edce52e412e0","tid":1079152,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"你仲有鍾意邊個／咩作品？<br />\n分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf7bae5bcace79a6965a79e432b4a5840781be","tid":1079152,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike