3Fsa%3Di%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjxhdmGmrzhAhWOzoUKHSQmCzEQjRx6BAgBEAU%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fmagazine.art21.org%252F2011%252F02%252F01%252Fart-design-and-clocks%252F%26psig%3DAOvVaw2EaymJOlAzptZhTwBjqwtR%26ust%3D1554665391559957&h=9cedb873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺1991年，美籍古巴裔藝術家FGT創作了Untitled (Perfect Lovers). 呢個作品有兩個一樣嘅時鐘，平排喺一面粉藍色嘅牆。呢兩個鐘本來顯示嘅時間喺一樣的，但其實其中一個嘅速度係稍稍快了，慢慢佢地顯示嘅時間就會出現差別，越來越大嘅差別。<br />\n呢個作品反映生命同愛係愛滋病面前嘅脆弱。FGT嘅伴侶係一個愛滋病患者，喺呢個作品完成不久就過世了。FGT自己係1996年都死於愛滋病。<br />\n可能大家對愛滋病好反感，但我覺得呢個作品係最觸動我嘅概念藝術。對我來講，佢嘅意思係人同人之間微妙得無法觀察嘅分別，愛侶／朋友／人與自己希望成為嘅自己兩者慢慢越走越遠的。真係令人好心痛。藝術真係好神奇，兩個時鐘就可以探索人靈魂嘅深處。"},{"pid":"3dbfc7467e5e092d7928501d08ffab197933892f","tid":1079152,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjdqtr7nbzhAhWox4UKHfH5BHkQjRx6BAgBEAU&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moma.org%2Fcollection%2Fworks%2F81074&amp;psig=AOvVaw2n3N2rZqDbb99agEXjXfC2&amp;ust=1554666442217211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjdqtr7nbzhAhWox4UKHfH5BHkQjRx6BAgBEAU%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.moma.org%252Fcollection%252Fworks%252F81074%26psig%3DAOvVaw2n3N2rZqDbb99agEXjXfC2%26ust%3D1554666442217211&h=37145c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試另一個link"},{"pid":"b38b316d7ff0aa8ae81431af90734c834226a66f","tid":1079152,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dbfc7467e5e092d7928501d08ffab197933892f","tid":1079152,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjdqtr7nbzhAhWox4UKHfH5BHkQjRx6BAgBEAU&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moma.org%2Fcollection%2Fworks%2F81074&amp;psig=AOvVaw2n3N2rZqDbb99agEXjXfC2&amp;ust=1